23(3): 211&ndash;214. doi:10.1353/ppp.2016.0020</li>

<li>Wakefield, Jerome C., 1992, &ldquo;The Concept of Mental Disorder:
On the Boundary between Biological Facts and Social Values&rdquo;.,
<em>American Psychologist</em>, 47(3): 373&ndash;388.
doi:10.1037/0003-066X.47.3.373</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1997, &ldquo;Diagnosing DSM-IV&mdash;Part
I: DSM-IV and the Concept of Disorder&rdquo;, <em>Behaviour Research
