doi:10.1016/S0005-7967(97)00018-1</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2012, &ldquo;Editorial: DSM-5: Proposed
Changes to Depressive Disorders&rdquo;, <em>Current Medical Research
