204(8): 606&ndash;613. doi:10.1097/NMD.0000000000000511</li>

<li>Wiggins, Osborne P. and Michael A. Schwartz, 2011,
&ldquo;Phenomenological Psychiatry Needs a Big Tent&rdquo;,
<em>Philosophy, Psychiatry, &amp; Psychology</em>, 18(1): 31&ndash;32.
doi:10.1353/ppp.2011.0013</li>

<li>Wilkinson, Stephen, 2000, &ldquo;Is &lsquo;Normal Grief&rsquo; a
Mental Disorder?&rdquo;, <em>The Philosophical Quarterly</em>,
50(200): 289&ndash;304. doi:10.1111/j.0031-8094.2000.00186.x</li>

<li>Worrell, Franklin and Alison Denham, 2016, &ldquo;Fragments of the
Self: Dissociation, Agency, and Integration&rdquo;, in Moseley and
